name: Mintendo Game Boi
description:
It’s Christmas Day, you’ve got a new toy.

The slick and sexy brick, Game Boi.

The shell is grey, the screen is green.

There’s black and blue, no inbetween.

The A, B Buttons are dark Magenta.

With grey and squishy start n selecta.

The contrast scrolls, the volume too.

An odd cable hole connects up two.

Four batteries go in the back hatch. 

Hear a snap as you close the latch. 

Push the cartridge in the top. 

All the way till you feel it stop.

Cup your hands and hold on tight. 

Then slide the switch from left to right.
